description:
As a merchant
  I want to set up invoice setting
  so that I can see split order invoice setting toggle
name: Split order re-invoice setting toggle

elements.name: Check message on Order Split Page when split-order-invoice-setting-toggle off.

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct admin email to email field
I fill correct admin password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Order Setting Page
I check and click invoice toggle off
I should see Nat No field
I fill Nat No to Nat No field
I select Donation Recipient of Donation Recipient dropdown
I fill 'SLINE02' to website code field
I fill '4DDC6C4EE' to api password field
I select tax type dropdown option included 'Taxable' of tax type dropdown

embeddings.data: {"retryCount":1,"elementTexts":["Zero-tax-rate- Not exported by customs","Zero-tax-rate- Exported by customs","Taxable"],"text":"Taxable"}
